The paper deals with the security and accuracy of cancelable biometric schemes, which are related to cryptography and computer vision. Therefore, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques, which are covered by cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses hashing functions, which are related to information theory, making cs.IT (Information Theory) a possible category as well.
